query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('android-studio',
'delphi',
'django',
'html5',
'laravel',
'node.js',
'qt',
'reference-request',
'sql-server',
'ubuntu',
'windows',
'winforms',
'веб-программирование',
'строки')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Benefactor',
'Cleanup',
'Disciplined',
'Enlightened',
'Enthusiast',
'Excavator',
'Fanatic',
'Good Answer',
'Good Question',
'Organizer')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('apple',
'mathoverflow',
'ru')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
